nodes.text: An Unidentified male Human inmate was a male Human criminal that was sentenced to a prison term in the Armand Isard Correctional Facility. In 44 ABY, he and several comrades, under the orders of Mon Calamari thief Furan confronted former Jedi Tahiri Veila, who was sentenced to the same prison. He was soundly beaten by the former Jedi Knight.
